\nin tho world, with tho exception of\nthat maintained by the Rockefellers\nfer the selection and care of their\nown personal investments. Mr.\nWyckoff, who \"heads the staff, has\ncollected a force of men of long ex\nperience in research work, author\nities on meney, credit, investment\nconditions and other economic sub\njects; attorneys, statisticians and ex\npert accountants; rnehcanical, rain\ninp and public utility engineers; oil\ngeedogists and enpineers; experts in\nrailroads and public utilities and in\nsteed, equipment, autmobil and\nedher industries; authorities o tech\nnical matters pertaining to tho\nwhole broad ranpe of industrial and\nsecurity market operations.\nThe object of the Richard D.\nWyckoff Analytical Staff is to de\ntermine the value of a security be\nfore recommending it fer investment\nby examining and analyzing it from\nnumere.us standpoints, such as or\nganization, management, finances,\ncharacter of industry, competition,\npermanency of demand, trend of\ngrowth, earning power, dividend\nrecord, distribution of its securities,\ntechnical position of Its shares, etc..\nas well as such other considerations\nwhich enter into the makinjr of\nsafe, profitable investments, like the\npresent and probable future state of\npe neral business, money conditions,\nposition and tendency of future\nprices, markets, etc.\nZ7U5Z lIT. jv\n9\nMr\nM-0\n9\nft\n49\nJ\nto\nJ\nT\n\nI 1 I u\njs t\nI\ns\n4. m\nFRANK\n113 S. Michigan St.\nMONEY AND\nFINANCE\nCredit Situation Easing\nBusiness Depression Re\nleases Huge Sum Expan\nsion Will Absorb Available\nSupply for Years to Come.\nThe money tension noticeably\neaslnp. Wide-spread price cutting\nand business depression will release\nmore, than 5 1.00. 000. 000 perhaps\nmore than 12.000,000.000 accom\nplishing what the federal reserve\nboard thought best not to attempt;\na sudd n sharp reduction in the vol\nume of credit and etirrency out\nstanding. Tho position of time\nmoney in New Ytrk has changed.\nHank cleari